  "id" : "api/animations/stagger",
  "title" : "stagger",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"stagger\">stagger</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label experimental\">experimental</label>\n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/animations\">@angular/animations</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a> } from <a href=\"api/animations\">'@angular/animations'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L1098-L1181\">animations/src/animation_metadata.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\nfunction <a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a>(timings: string | number, <a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a>: <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationMetadata</a> | <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationMetadata</a>[]): <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationStaggerMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationStaggerMetadata</a>;\n</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6vf6kqbht9rtb2rhmxzq35wby\"><code><a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a></code> 是一个动画专用函数，设计用于 Angular 的动画 DSL 语言。它旨在用于动画 \n<a href=\"api/animations/query\">query()</a> 中，并通过在每个查询项目动画完成后发出计时间隔来工作。</p>\n<h3 id=\"usage\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bqkiuc1612srggyr16nss2hrq\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>用法</h3>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6lwrycug7lts9rgo8pwr29u0o\">在下面的示例中，有一个容器元素，它包装了由 ngFor 标记出来的项目列表。容器元素包含一个动画触发器，该触发器稍后将被设置为查询每个内部项目。</p>\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&lt;!-- list.component.html --&gt;\n&lt;button (click)=\"toggle()\"&gt;Show / Hide Items&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;hr /&gt;\n&lt;div [@listAnimation]=\"items.length\"&gt;\n  &lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgForOf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a>=\"let item of items\"&gt;\n    {{ item }}\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9rznt8ed2bb5lk8fqmfpbm87a\">此组件代码如下所示：</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nimport {<a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/transition\" class=\"code-anchor\">transition</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/animate\" class=\"code-anchor\">animate</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>, <a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a>} from '@angular/animations';\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  templateUrl: 'list.component.html',\n  animations: [\n    <a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>('listAnimation', [\n       //...\n    ])\n  ]\n})\nclass ListComponent {\n  items = [];\n\n  showItems() {\n    this.items = [0,1,2,3,4];\n  }\n\n  hideItems() {\n    this.items = [];\n  }\n\n  toggle() {\n    this.items.length ? this.hideItems() : this.showItems();\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8qm4zviq1xlwn4d86gj6g1vus\">现在是动画触发器代码：</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n<a href=\"api/animations/trigger\" class=\"code-anchor\">trigger</a>('listAnimation', [\n  <a href=\"api/animations/transition\" class=\"code-anchor\">transition</a>('* =&gt; *', [ // each time the binding value changes\n    <a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>(':leave', [\n      <a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a>(100, [\n        <a href=\"api/animations/animate\" class=\"code-anchor\">animate</a>('0.5s', <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>({ opacity: 0 }))\n      ])\n    ]),\n    <a href=\"api/animations/query\" class=\"code-anchor\">query</a>(':enter', [\n      <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>({ opacity: 0 }),\n      <a href=\"api/animations/stagger\" class=\"code-anchor\">stagger</a>(100, [\n        <a href=\"api/animations/animate\" class=\"code-anchor\">animate</a>('0.5s', <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a>({ opacity: 1 }))\n      ])\n    ])\n  ])\n])\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3lprxyy1955d58flfw7203ek4\">现在，每次添加/删除项目时，都会运行不透明度淡入动画，或者每个删除的项目都会淡出。当这些动画中的任何一个发生时，将在每个项目的动画开始后应用一个交错效果。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationStaggerMetadata\n - api/animations/animateChild\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationStaggerMetadata\n - api/animations/animate\n - api/animations/animation\n - api/animations/query\n - api/animations/stagger#description\n - api/animations/stagger#stagger\n - api/animations/stagger#usage\n - api/animations/style\n - api/animations/transition\n - api/animations/trigger\n - api/common/NgForOf\n - api/core/Component\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L1098-L1181\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/animations\n-->"
